## Validation Checklist

Before publishing any post containing a URL:

- [ ] `utm_source` — correct platform and account type
- [ ] `utm_medium` — matches traffic type
- [ ] `utm_campaign` — `[theme]_[product]` format, **no date**
- [ ] `utm_content` — `YYYYMMDD_post[N]` for organic; creative identifier for ads
- [ ] `utm_term` — included only for paid campaigns
- [ ] All values lowercase — no capital letters
- [ ] Underscores only — no spaces or hyphens
- [ ] Parameters separated by `&`
- [ ] Date in `utm_content` matches actual publishing date
- [ ] Post number correct (increments for multiple posts on same day)

---

## Common Mistakes

❌ No UTMs at all
```
https://www.stonerise.tech/request-demo
```

❌ Date inside campaign name
```
utm_campaign=202602_invoice_ai_procurement  →  utm_campaign=invoice_ai_procurement
```

❌ Missing account type in source
```
utm_source=linkedin  →  utm_source=linkedin_michael
```

❌ Wrong date format in content
```
utm_content=week1_post1   →  utm_content=20260304_post1
utm_content=feb3_post1    →  utm_content=20260304_post1
utm_content=03022026_post1  →  utm_content=20260304_post1
```

❌ Capital letters or spaces
```
utm_source=LinkedIn          →  utm_source=linkedin_company
utm_content=20260304 post1   →  utm_content=20260304_post1
```

