## Tools

**Build UTMs:** https://ga-dev-tools.google/campaign-url-builder/

**Shorten URLs (recommended)** — long UTM strings look messy in posts. Always shorten the **full URL including all UTM parameters**, never the bare base URL.

| Tool | URL | Notes |
|------|-----|-------|
| Bitly | https://bitly.com | 50 links/month free; custom slugs; click analytics |
| TinyURL | https://tinyurl.com | Free, unlimited, no analytics |
| Rebrandly | https://www.rebrandly.com | Custom branded domains (paid) |

**LinkedIn note:** LinkedIn auto-shortens URLs over 23 characters via `lnkd.in`, which preserves UTM parameters. Using Bitly additionally gives a readable slug and extra click data.

**Shortening workflow:**
1. Build full URL with all UTMs
2. Paste into Bitly → set custom slug (e.g. `sr-demo-mar04`)
3. Use the short link in your post

