## New Post Template

```
[POST CONTENT]

CTA: [Call to action text]

Link: https://www.stonerise.tech/[page]?utm_source=[SOURCE]&utm_medium=[MEDIUM]&utm_campaign=[CAMPAIGN]&utm_content=[YYYYMMDD_postN]

UTM breakdown:
- source:   [platform]_[account]
- medium:   organic_social / paid_social / email / cpc
- campaign: [theme]_[product]  ← NO date here
- content:  [YYYYMMDD]_post[N] ← full date here
```

